<project xml:id="cool-ubicaYMarca" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Ubica y marca</title>

<statement>
  <p>Ubica y marca <m>\frac{1}{8}</m> en la recta numérica. Explica tu razonamiento.</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151157">
    <shortdescription>recta numérica de 0 a 2, con las unidades marcadas</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151158">
      <shortdescription>recta numérica de 0 a 2 con 1/8 marcado.</shortdescription>
    </image>
    <p>
      I know that 8 one-eighths are in 1, so I partitioned the number line from 0 to 1 into 8 equal parts and labeled the end of the first eighth.
    </p>
  </solution>


